International Hotels May Increase Dividend, Sunday Times Reports

-- B y   M i c h e l l e   E .   F r a z e r
-- 
2011-02-13T07:15:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-13/international-hotels-may-increase-dividend-sunday-times-reports.html
International Hotels Group Plc may
increase its final dividend by about 10 percent, the Sunday
Times reported, without saying where it got the information.  The hotel group may also report plans to refurbish its
Crowne Plaza chain, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michelle E. Frazer in London at 
 mfrazer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
